> **This is a starting-point template, not legal advice.** Financial-
> services subprocessors require evidence of safeguards proportional
> to the data sensitivity (typically SOC 2 Type II at minimum;
> SOC 1 Type II for vendors involved in financial reporting; ISO
> 27001 as an alternative). Verify each vendor's current terms,
> regions, and audit-report currency before relying on entries below.

